  description: "socket.socket.accept.__code__.co_stacksize.__class__.__name__.__eq__('int') == True — co_stacksize is always an integer indicating required VM stack space for Python code objects; accept is a pure Python method in Lib/socket.py; no prior socket spec checks accept.__code__.co_stacksize; first co_stacksize anchor for any socket.socket method"
  category: code_objects
